	**************************************************
	*						 *
	*	       1.2 SERIES NEWS			 *
	*						 *
	**************************************************


		CHANGES IN R VERSION 1.2.1

NEW FEATURES

    o	Added a "clip" option to the "image" method that toggles
    	whether chrtomosomes are shown full length or are shrunk to be
    	the real size relative to Chromosome 1.

DOCUMENTATION

    o	Minor changes to graphing routines to try to achieve better
        automated placement of chromosome labels (see vignettes).

    o	Clarified that cytoband locations are the same in several
        genome builds.


		CHANGES IN R VERSION 1.1.1

NEW FEATURES

    o	Added a "preclean" function to delete recurrent non-standard
        phrases from input karyotypes.


		CHANGES IN R VERSION 1.0.0

NEW FEATURES

    o	Initial release of the package.
